Dwarves are a noble race of squat demihumans who usually dwell 
underground.  They are great builders of tools and cities, and of 
weapons when the time comes for war.  They love precious metals 
and gems, and some people call them greedy.  Dwarves are a very 
hardy folk, and quite strong.  They have to be in order to maintain 
their extensive mining operations.  They do not like magic, and have 
not much aptitude for it either.  Their fingers are short, like the rest 
of them, making feats of manual dexterity difficult.  Dwarves are 
often bluntly honest, which does not endear them to many, and 
taciturn.

Dwarves have a small amount on innate magic resistance.
 
Dwarves cannot join the following guilds:  Druid, Mage, Necromancer,
Swashbuckler, Thief.
